message.body: Hello, would you like to have a conversation?
Hi, yes I would
Oh that's great. How are you?
I feel like I've known you for years now.
Don't you feel the same? It's like we are soul mate texters
Okay I couldn't help joking. I just wanted to get this text experiment over with and I don't really feel like getting to know anyone over text. I actually hate texting, and prefer calls.
LOL I know its pretty strange texting a stranger
Did you do the experiment where you talk I strangers over calls? I actually liked that one.
Also what's with the trend in research to "enter you into a drawing" rather than just pay for participation? I call bullshoot.
Yea thats annoying talking would be an interesting study
So do you watch television? What pop culture things might we have to talk about/ what are your hobbies that I might care about?
I do I watch a bunch of random shows really
Which?
Lets see, once upon a time, community, 30 rock, random reality shows, arrested dev,
I like most of those too. I heard arrested development producer (?) in an interview yesterday. Thy labeled his type of humor "absurdity" I think.
That sounds about right
You're not very good at this are you?
Nice
Look we're all here for the money
I now but im just having a busy day you texted me at work and ive been on the move all day
I totally understand
We had tacos for dinner. They were delicious
So what do you like to do?
Eat tacos
I'm a neurosurgeon so I need some down time and tacos are perfect
Are you a neurosurgeon too?
No I'm a social worker
That's way cooler. I was of course lying. I'm actually an astrophysicist.
sorry I'm messing around so much. I'm feeling very strange today
Yea you seen very strange lol
it's okay, no need for the lol. What do you want to talk about?
Lets see I guess I could bombard you with random stories of varied subjects.
Subject one: getting hit on while on public transit.
Sure!
Isn't that the BEST???
So ive noticed a trend I only get hit on public transit if im in the shittiest mood. I mean everything went wrong at work, its too damn hot, I hate life
no one talk to me just absolute shittiest fuck you humanity mood
Yes life should be cold and good not hit and bad
*hot
Maybe you shouldn't say fuck to me. We just met.
I'm very religious. I'm a religious potato farmer in the Midwest.
Just fucking with you. I'm still listening.
Youre bit of a pathological liar to consider yourself very religious dont you think?
Don't you analyze me devil woman!
Yea I figured. Anyway me in bitch mood has attracked an ex con, a married father of two, and a guy who felt me saying-just leave me alone please- was rud
e enough to warrant the response
`you dont have to be so rude I bet you wouldnr be if I was trying t
o rob you.
I find being polite to ex cons usually works in my favor.
I forget how this works, do we need a certain number of texts or characters or lines?
You are sending me each text twice and thrice
I feel like maybe there is some disconnect hear
Here
You must be purty
Yea ive been getting your text twice/thrice
Oh, how delightfully unexpected!
Ohhhh program glitch
Did you rob them then???
For good measure, I mean?
That wouldve have been a good idea ill remember that for the next time im pissed on the train
This makes me wonder if guys see me mad and think `challenge' accep
ted or if im just really shitty at facial expressions
